HEADWORD: Bronzine
<hw>Bronz"ine</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A metal so
prepared as to have the appearance of bronze.</def> --
<def2><pos>a.</pos> <def>Made of bronzine; resembling bronze;
bronzelike.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
